크롤링¶

In [7]:
page_num = 1

last_page_num = 20

title_f = []
date_f = []
article_f = []

while True:

    url = f"https://www.mk.co.kr/news/stock/?page={page_num*10+1}"
    response = requests.get(url)
    soup = BeautifulSoup(response.content.decode('euc-kr','replace'),'html.parser')
    
    df = pd.DataFrame(columns=["date","title","article"])

    news_list = soup.select('#container_left > div.list_area > dl')
    for news in news_list:
    
        # 뉴스 제목
        title = news.select_one('.article_list > dt.tit') 
        for tit in title:
            title_f.append(title.text)
    
        # 일자
        date = news.select('.article_list > dd.desc > span.date')
        for dat in date:
            date_f.append(date[-1].text)
        
        #본문 내용
        sources = news.select_one('.article_list > dt.tit > a')
        news_r = requests.get(sources.attrs['href'])
        news_sp = BeautifulSoup(news_r.content.decode('euc-kr','replace'),'html.parser')
        article = news_sp.select('div#Content > div.left_content > div#article_body > div')
        for art in article:
            article_f.append(article)
    if page_num == 20*(last_page_num-1)+1:
        break
        
    page_num += 20
